OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mostly dry with
OL,6,Fbright spells and some hazy sunshine
OL,7,Fin the east. Windy and cloudy in the
OL,8,Ffar northwest, with perhaps some rain
OL,9,Fover the Isles.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FFor many, it will be a dry
OL,12,Fnight with patchy cloud and clear
OL,13,Fspells. Cloudy with strong winds over
OL,14,Fthe Western Isles however with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy and windy over the
OL,18,FWestern Isles with outbreaks of rain.
OL,19,FElsewhere will stay dry with bright
OL,20,Fand sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
