OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,6,FMonday and Tuesday with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain. Heavier rain spreading east
OL,8,Flater Tuesday. Rain clears Wednesday
OL,9,Fto bright spells and showers. Winds
OL,10,Flight Monday, strong on Tuesday and
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
